text: Are you interested in Save the Children?
What is that?
It's an international organization that promotes children's rights, provides relief and helps support children in developing countries.
They sound interesting.  When were they established?
let me check that for you. is that important info for you?
I was just curious.  It's always good to work with an organization that has been around for some time.
I think it says 1919! so that's a while!
Good enough for me.
are you interested in donating to save the children?
Yes, I think I am
How much do you like to donate to the charity now?
What's the minimum?
Well, it comes from your task payment I think.
Ok, I'd like to donate $.50
That's a great offer!
I know it's small but it's something.
It's fine. The research team will collect all donations and send it to Save the Children.
Ok.  So, how do we proceed?
I'm not sure I think maybe they'll see the chat.
Oh....I thought you were involved somehow....my mistake.
No, you agreed, so that's all we need to do. Thanks for chatting!
